text: anyone else been using apple music?
I tried but it’s full of tiny annoyances and bugs. Went back to Spotify.
And it’s so slow.
hm, hasn’t been slow for me.
i have been wanting to leave rdio for a while but never made the full switch to spotify
but i will be switching to apple music when the trial is over. Rdio has just gotten worse and worse.
and the For You tab on Apple Music is spot on.
for me anyway
but the UI is not great
but i’m confident that it will improve

The main thing for me is the apps. Both Mac and iPhone apps try to do way too much. I like how Spotify is just for music, there’re no movies or podcasts and there isn’t any confusion over which music is mine (bought).
yeah i would agree with that
theres some weird transitional sloppiness for them to work out

Final thing is that Apple stuff seems to be getting worse and not better so I don’t have much hope for music. I really hope it gets better but every other Apple app and service I use has gotten significantly worse in the last year and 1/2.
